    title: 'Hotel Construction Guide: Building Hotels And Resorts In Tanzania And Zanzibar',
    description: 'Complete guide to hotel construction in Tanzania and Zanzibar covering design, materials, regulations and contractor selection for beach resorts, safari lodges and urban hotels.',
